_sText:
Here's my first Iceskate map. It's pretty simple, both teams on different sides. I decided to leave it as it is because I didnt want to make it very complicated. Just simple.

________

Basically, The T's And CT's have to face off against eachother with knifes and skate around. There is a deagle in the middle of the map but it only has 7 bullets, use your shots wisely.
